'''Kevin Thompson''' is an actor who played [[Chubbray]], an [[Ewok]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]. He performed his own stunts.<ref name="Insider 217" /> In [[1984]], he played [[Chukha-Trok/Legends|Chukha-Trok]] in the movie ''[[Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure]]''<ref name="Caravan of Courage">''[[Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure]]''</ref> and worked as a stuntman in the [[1985]] sequel ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''.<ref name="Battle of Endor">''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''</ref>

